Banner.Title: We understand the complexity of the Construction Business
Banner.Description: Projects are unique, Sites are unique, Scale is variable, Workers change, subcontractors change along with cost and timeline. Did we miss anything? We have designed domo to handle all of these for you and much more!

AboutSustainability.Title: Keep regulators happy with enhanced compliance.
AboutSustainability.subTitle: Construction projects spend more on worker comp fines than any other industry in the U.S. Reduce this exposure by accurately tracking.

About_us.title: Save on labor costs with Contactless Clocking.
About_us.description: Facial biometric clocks allow for the most accurate and super fast clocking experience. When there are no long lines to clock-in and out, workers comply more and you get accurate data. Manage labor costs more efficiently. Workers love interacting with FR Clocks. Build Employee trust and step into the future with Workerly!
